    <data key="d0">Vigod Aqua Water Management Platform</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CE03UMddoYU</data>
    <data key="d2">IoT platform processing 27M daily events from 100k water meters. Reduces downstream processing load by 60% using an in-memory Redis deduplication/filtering step, leading to a 25% cost reduction during scale-up.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
